Sentence: Ligand engagement of specific membrane receptors such as TNFR1, CD40, RANK, and TLR4 trigger the recruitment of specific adaptor proteins ( TNF receptor 1 - associated death domain protein ( TRADD), MyD88, MAL, TIR domain - containing adaptor - inducing IFNbeta ( TRIF)), kinases ( RIP1, IRAK1, IRAK4), and ubiquitin ligases ( TRAF2, TRAF6, cIAP1, cIAP2) to the receptor.
